name: Steven Nason
text: Actually Great Pizza Hut. I THINK OWNERS RUN IT PERSONALLY WITH EXTRA STAFF BUT HANDS DOWN GREAT EXPERIENCE. SERVICE WAS AWESOME and FACILITY WAS CLEAN!! THANKS

name: Felis Contreras
text: Great food!!

name: Barbara Foote
text: Best pizza ever.  You all really need to go back to having customers eat inside not just take out.  To me that ruined everything about Pizza Hut.  Friendly employees.

name: Braxton Brown
text: Always hot food, dine in service is fast and always when needed, you'll never find yourself wondering where a waiter is when your drink is empty or it is time to pay.

name: Jason Wait
text: Service and food quality has went way down hill over the past year.  Used to be the best Pizza Hut in the area but now I'm not so sure anymore

name: MLP CARDBOARD STOPMOTION
text: Great taste but off the wall price

name: Zodar #
text: Best damn Pizza Hut I have been in a longing time. Clean, friendly, and food was good. Plus finally a pizza hut with customer WIFI!

name: Terri Plain
text: The waitress was taking other table's orders that had arrived after we did, so I finally had to walk up to the desk to put our order in. The Super Supreme pizza although was very good and better than expected. The coffee was also very good We were disappointed there was NOT a salad bar at this location.

name: tb day
text: Our sodas were flat. One of our orders never came out. We had to get it to go because the rest of us were done eating by the time it even came out. Not impressed the last several times i have eaten at pizza hut in oklahoma!

name: Merceds13 sanchez
text: They were nice and there was great food

name: Mark Hance
text: Good pizza, friendly workers

name: Becca Green
text: Overall this location is okay. It depends on when you go on how the food and service is.

name: Barbara Broyles
text: Great subs and soups

name: Mary Peacock
text: Good food and service.

name: Baby Gangsta13
text: Clean bathrooms great food and awesome waiters

name: Ben Phelps
text: It was good service and very kind waiters

name: Steve and Maria Taylor
text: Thin crust supreme pizza was so good!

name: Melinda Jordan
text: We came in and the workers were talking with friends and not working. Then we ordered an appetizer and she made a fuss when we asked for ranch. Then when our pizza came it wasn't good at all. We order half backyard bbq chicken and it had no bbq sauce on it at all. Thank God we were just driving through and won't be returning.

name: Michael Tipton
text: Small town Pizza Hut.  Great place.

name: Scott Miller
text: Food was acceptable. Maybe training newbies but was an hour after arrived before our medium meat lovers arrived.

name: Mike Atkinson
text: Had try yell to get someone's attention every time we needed drink refill. Didn't listen to order, totally never order one thing we order. Everyone was either hiding in the back or talking with a friend in the dinning area.

name: JR Ochoa
text: Good food but bad service

name: Jonathan Olivarez
